The keyboard becomes a real-time AI communication assistant.

Instead of typing manually, users get instant AI-generated reactions, replies, and actions.

Example moment:

Friend message

"We're going out tonight. You coming?"

Keyboard immediately suggests

🔥 LETS GOOO
🙌 I'm down
😂😂😂
Drinks tonight?

User taps → message sent instantly.

This is the "one tap conversation" experience.

Core Product Principles

The prototype should demonstrate three core capabilities.

1. Context Awareness

The keyboard reads the conversation and understands:

• tone
• topic
• intent
• emotional signals

Example signals

party
funny
planning
question
2. Intent Detection

The AI predicts what the user wants to do.

Possible intents

react
reply
translate
summarize
plan
search
3. AI Action Layer

Instead of typing, the keyboard suggests actions.

Examples

Find nearby bars
Translate message
Generate meme reply
Summarize conversation
